				not for the nation only, but also 
				<crossref let="b" cid="c43011052.2">
				</crossref>
				to gather into one the children of God who are scattered abroad.
			</verse>
			<marker class="begin-verse" mid="v43011053">
			</marker>
			<verse num="53">
				So from that day on they 
				<crossref let="c" cid="c43011053.1">
